text: Pedro Vázquez Llenin (born 6 August 1996) is a Spanish sprint canoeist.Profile He won a medal at the 2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships.2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships results ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships medalists in kayak Category:Spanish male canoeists
